message.body: Whoopsie daisy. This wednesday is a monday class schedule...so guess im missing class hah. Tis ok with me :) Another day with my darling
I'm not! :-p How's your morning going, my love?
Good. Maddie fell asleep and kim and I are just talking! How was work?!
Haha what what?! I thoguht she wasnt supposed to take morning naps anymore hah. Sounds pretty awesome. Glad youve got Kim with ya. Work wasnt so much fun. Tired
Better! Still need a good days sleep, but all is well :) Just cant wait to see you tomorrow. At school printing tix now
Me neither!!!! I had horrible dreams last night. Like AWFUL! I need you to sleep with me.
Oh baby :-( again bad dreams?? I dont like that. Not one bit. Im coming, my love. Hold you the whole night
Meeee neither! But, right now...i go bed :) Night beauty! Mwah! Keep enjoying the day!
Baby. Pack warm for tomorrow, wed, and Thursday. It's only going to be in the 20s!!!
Made it on the bus! Already freezing my buns off haha. I say you stay in bed and i'll meet you under the blankets :) Was hoping they cancelled work for ya
Me too but unfortunately it's not snowy enough! Haha. Maybe I'll get to leave early though I doubt it.
Psaw its plenty snowy enough! Even we have 3 inches. You stay home!
We don't! Haha. I didn't wear snow boots either. They said less than an inch here!!!!!
Oh...well dang...that stinks. But guess if you dont have your boots, its a very good thing! But, see you soon soon and have a good day! I go nap now :)
Okay! I love you. Be safe and soon soon we'll be sleeping under the covers togetha!!
Woohoooo! Cant wait!! Seriously haha. Thats all i want right now. Love you too, darling :)
